    <param.description>The intention is to give a quick and visual introduction to the concept of digitisation, that is, what happens when we have a computer handling signals produced by a continuous system. Clearly, the computer can only handle signals at discrete time instants and this changes both the nature of the signal and the information contained.</param.description>
